<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">hat David Calderwood, who&s;e <HI>Altare Dama&s;cenum,</HI> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">rinted in both Latin and Engli&s;h, had &s;o galled the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">pi&s;copal party, had died in Holland, Patrick Scot, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> is &s;aid, by his maje&s;ty's direction, publi&s;hed a re|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">antation in his name; and to prevent his refuting it, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ent to Holland to &s;eek him out, and murder him <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">f he were &s;till alive.</P>
