<P>During the&s;e litigations in England, the Genera<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> A&s;&s;embly met at Edinburgh in Augu&s;t 1647, has e&s;tabli&s;hed &s;ome directions for &s;ecret and family wor+&s;hip;
